trans-unit.source: Provides a thread-safe collection that contains channel dispatchers.
trans-unit.target: Fornece uma coleção de seguro para thread com dispatchers de canal.

trans-unit.source: This collection is used by <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase> to manage the channel dispatchers associated with the host.
trans-unit.target: Esta coleção é utilizada pelo <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>para gerir os dispatchers canal associados com o anfitrião.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>

trans-unit.source: A ChannelDispatcherCollection is created when <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.%23ctor%2A> is called and the collection can be accessed using the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Um ChannelDispatcherCollection é criado quando <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.%23ctor%2A>denomina-se e a coleção pode ser acedida através de <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: The collection contains <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> objects (and not just instances of <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>) because it is also used by developers who want to keep the [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]programming model but replace the system-provided runtime.
trans-unit.target: A coleção contém <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>objetos (e não apenas as instâncias do <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher>) porque também é utilizado pelos programadores que pretendem manter o [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], mas substitua o tempo de execução fornecidos pelo sistema de modelo de programação.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcher> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>

trans-unit.source: They derive a class from <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> and extend <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> (which inherits from <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>) by overriding <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.InitializeRuntime%2A>, adding instances of the class derived from <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> to <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Derivam de uma classe a partir <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>e expandir <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>(que herda de <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>) através da substituição <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.InitializeRuntime%2A>, adicionar as instâncias da classe derivada de <xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>para <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.ChannelDispatchers%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase.InitializeRuntime%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase> </xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Dispatcher.ChannelDispatcherBase>

trans-unit.source: This class has no public constructors and is not intended to be used outside of the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>.
trans-unit.target: Esta classe tem não foram construtores públicos e não se destina a ser utilizado fora <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHost>

trans-unit.target: Remove todos os dispatchers do canal da coleção.

trans-unit.target: O anfitrião do serviço associado à coleção de emissor canal está fechado.
